Package it.polimi.se2019.controller

Class VirtualView

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.view.View
      • it.polimi.se2019.controller.VirtualView
  • public class VirtualView
extends View
    Virtual view used by the model and server to:
  • Send updates to the client,using viewUpdater
  • Receive and compute events from the client, using requestDispatcher
    • Every client has its own VirtualView
